{"tha-ap548:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap548:0.2":"Bhaddiyavagga ","tha-ap548:0.3":"Kaludayittheraapadana ","tha-ap548:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap548:1.2":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","tha-ap548:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap548:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","tha-ap548:2.1":"Nayakanam varo sattha, ","tha-ap548:2.2":"gunagunavidu jino; ","tha-ap548:2.3":"Katannu katavedi ca, ","tha-ap548:2.4":"titthe yojeti panine. ","tha-ap548:3.1":"Sabbannutena nanena, ","tha-ap548:3.2":"tulayitva dayasayo; ","tha-ap548:3.3":"Deseti pavaram dhammam, ","tha-ap548:3.4":"anantagunasancayo. ","tha-ap548:4.1":"Sa kadaci mahaviro, ","tha-ap548:4.2":"anantajinasamsari; ","tha-ap548:4.3":"Deseti madhuram dhammam, ","tha-ap548:4.4":"catusaccupasanhitam. ","tha-ap548:5.1":"Sutvana tam dhammavaram, ","tha-ap548:5.2":"adimajjhantasobhanam; ","tha-ap548:5.3":"Panasatasahassanam, ","tha-ap548:5.4":"dhammabhisamayo ahu. ","tha-ap548:6.1":"Ninnadita tada bhumi, ","tha-ap548:6.2":"gajjimsu ca payodhara; ","tha-ap548:6.3":"Sadhukaram pavattimsu, ","tha-ap548:6.4":"devabrahmanarasura. ","tha-ap548:7.1":"‘Aho karuniko sattha, ","tha-ap548:7.2":"aho saddhammadesana; ","tha-ap548:7.3":"Aho bhavasamuddamhi, ","tha-ap548:7.4":"nimugge uddhari jino’. ","tha-ap548:8.1":"Evam pavedajatesu, ","tha-ap548:8.2":"sanaramarabrahmasu; ","tha-ap548:8.3":"Kulappasadakanaggam, ","tha-ap548:8.4":"savakam vannayi jino. ","tha-ap548:9.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap548:9.2":"jatomaccakule ahum; ","tha-ap548:9.3":"Pasadiko dassaniyo, ","tha-ap548:9.4":"pahutadhanadhannava. ","tha-ap548:10.1":"Hamsaramamupeccaham, ","tha-ap548:10.2":"vanditva tam tathagatam; ","tha-ap548:10.3":"Sunitva madhuram dhammam, ","tha-ap548:10.4":"karam katva ca tadino. ","tha-ap548:11.1":"Nipacca padamuleham, ","tha-ap548:11.2":"imam vacanamabravim; ","tha-ap548:11.3":"‘Kulappasadakanaggo, ","tha-ap548:11.4":"yo taya santhuto mune. ","tha-ap548:12.1":"Tadiso homaham vira, ","tha-ap548:12.2":"buddhasetthassa sasane’; ","tha-ap548:12.3":"Tada mahakaruniko, ","tha-ap548:12.4":"sincanto vamatena mam. ","tha-ap548:13.1":"Aha mam ‘putta uttittha, ","tha-ap548:13.2":"lacchase tam manoratham; ","tha-ap548:13.3":"Katham nama jine karam, ","tha-ap548:13.4":"katvana viphalo siya. ","tha-ap548:14.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap548:14.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap548:14.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap548:14.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap548:15.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap548:15.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap548:15.3":"Udayi nama namena, ","tha-ap548:15.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap548:16.1":"Tam sutva mudito hutva, ","tha-ap548:16.2":"yavajivam tada jinam; ","tha-ap548:16.3":"Mettacitto paricarim, ","tha-ap548:16.4":"paccayehi vinayakam. ","tha-ap548:17.1":"Tena kammavipakena, ","tha-ap548:17.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap548:17.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap548:17.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap548:18.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","tha-ap548:18.2":"ramme kapilavatthave; ","tha-ap548:18.3":"Jato mahamaccakule, ","tha-ap548:18.4":"suddhodanamahipate. ","tha-ap548:19.1":"Tada ajayi siddhattho, ","tha-ap548:19.2":"ramme lumbinikanane; ","tha-ap548:19.3":"Hitaya sabbalokassa, ","tha-ap548:19.4":"sukhaya ca narasabho. ","tha-ap548:20.1":"Tadaheva aham jato, ","tha-ap548:20.2":"saha teneva vaddhito; ","tha-ap548:20.3":"Piyo sahayo dayito, ","tha-ap548:20.4":"viyatto nitikovido. ","tha-ap548:21.1":"Ekunatimso vayasa, ","tha-ap548:21.2":"nikkhamitva agarato; ","tha-ap548:21.3":"Chabbassam vitinametva, ","tha-ap548:21.4":"asi buddho vinayako. ","tha-ap548:22.1":"Jetva sasenakam maram, ","tha-ap548:22.2":"khepayitvana asave; ","tha-ap548:22.3":"Bhavannavam taritvana, ","tha-ap548:22.4":"buddho asi sadevake. ","tha-ap548:23.1":"Isivhayam gamitvana, ","tha-ap548:23.2":"vinetva pancavaggiye; ","tha-ap548:23.3":"Tato vinesi bhagava, ","tha-ap548:23.4":"gantva gantva tahim tahim. ","tha-ap548:24.1":"Veneyye vinayanto so, ","tha-ap548:24.2":"sanganhanto sadevakam; ","tha-ap548:24.3":"Upecca magadhe girim, ","tha-ap548:24.4":"viharittha tada jino. ","tha-ap548:25.1":"Tada suddhodanenaham, ","tha-ap548:25.2":"bhumipalena pesito; ","tha-ap548:25.3":"Gantva disva dasabalam, ","tha-ap548:25.4":"pabbajitvaraha ahum. ","tha-ap548:26.1":"Tada mahesim yacitva, ","tha-ap548:26.2":"papayim kapilavhayam; ","tha-ap548:26.3":"Tato puraham gantvana, ","tha-ap548:26.4":"pasadesim mahakulam. ","tha-ap548:27.1":"Jino tasmim gune tuttho, ","tha-ap548:27.2":"mam mahaparisaya so; ","tha-ap548:27.3":"Kulappasadakanaggam, ","tha-ap548:27.4":"pannapesi vinayako. ","tha-ap548:28.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap548:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap548:28.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap548:29.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap548:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap548:29.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap548:30.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap548:30.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap548:30.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap548:31.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kaludayi thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap548:32.1":"Kaludayittherassapadanam chattham. "}